    {
      "id": "PopularPost312299",
      "post_content": "One of the most powerful hosers ever printed, and the card that protected delicate combo pieces in decks like [Prosperity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prosperity)/[Cadaverous Bloom](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cadaverous Bloom), often considered one of the first true combo decks. It hoses all kinds of things, from countermagic (blue) to instant creature removal (black), which are weaknesses of green. The beauty of it was that you couldn't [Disenchant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant) it the turn it dropped either, so your only hope was to counter it. And with black's rich suite of discard, you could play [Coercion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Coercion) or the like to make sure you protected your City from countermagic before laying it down.  \n  \nThe art is also fantastic and evocative. It's also a green control card, which is sorely lacking in the game's history. This card gets a 5/5 for me, the perfect mix of subtlety, beauty and utility.",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost312299\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">One of the most powerful hosers ever printed, and the card that protected delicate combo pieces in decks like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prosperity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prosperity\">Prosperity</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cadaverous Bloom\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cadaverous Bloom\">Cadaverous Bloom</a>, often considered one of the first true combo decks.  It hoses all kinds of things, from countermagic (blue) to instant creature removal (black), which are weaknesses of green.  The beauty of it was that you couldn't <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Disenchant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant\">Disenchant</a> it the turn it dropped either, so your only hope was to counter it.  And with black's rich suite of discard, you could play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Coercion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Coercion\">Coercion</a> or the like to make sure you protected your City from countermagic before laying it down.<br/><br/>The art is also fantastic and evocative.  It's also a green control card, which is sorely lacking in the game's history.  This card gets a 5/5 for me, the perfect mix of subtlety, beauty and utility.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '312299'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1136\">Equinox523</span>\r\n                                (4/26/2013 7:39:57 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
